::Zardus::

Zardus enters the cargo hold, the crates of energon in front of him. He 
smiles, looking at the many crates.

"Each box contains 50 kilograms," he says, picking up a mostly filled box and 
putting it on the other side of the room.

"The rest are yours," he says, pointing to the other six crates, "Bonus 
included."
